<p>The judge told The Mirror: 'It was a dream of mine to work on American television. Everybody gets to a point where they get itchy feet, they want to try something new and be challenged.</p>

<p>'I like to step into an arena that makes me feel afraid – it's good for me. By stepping out of my comfort zone, great things come.</p>

<p>'I was really scared in the most amazing way. I can't wait for lockdown to be over so I can go back.'</p>

